setInfo.name: EX Sandstorm
setInfo.description: The second set in the EX Series, featuring desert and fossil-themed Pokémon. Introduces the famous Rare Candy trainer card and includes powerful fossil Pokémon like Armaldo and Cradily. Features Eeveelutions and the debut of several Generation III Pokémon-ex cards including Aggron ex and Gardevoir ex.
